---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs Endorsal — Which testimonial tool is right for you? | SocialProof" description="Endorsal starts at $29/mo. SocialProof is free to start and $9/mo Pro. Both automate testimonial collection — here's the honest comparison." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/endorsal">
<style>

    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: #3730a3; }
    .price-callout { display: inline-flex; gap: 2rem; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .price-callout .item { text-align: center; }
    .price-callout .item .price { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .price-callout .item .label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #777; margin-top: .2rem; }
    .price-callout .item.vouch .price { color: #4f46e5; }
    .price-callout .item.other .price { color: #dc2626; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .compare-table th { padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #888; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: #4f46e5; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 0.97rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .compare-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 500; }
    .yes { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .no { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
    .partial { color: #d97706; font-weight: 600; }
    .winner-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .winner-card { border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; }
    .winner-card.vouch { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #86efac; }
    .winner-card.other { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; }
    .winner-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 .75rem; }
    .winner-card ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    .winner-card li { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #444; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
    .savings-box { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .savings-box h3 { margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-size: 1rem; }
    .savings-box p { margin: 0; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .bottom-cta { text-align: center; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3rem 2rem; margin: 2rem auto; max-width: 900px; }
    .bottom-cta h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .bottom-cta p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.8); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .bottom-cta a { display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #4f46e5; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding: 1.25rem 0; }
    .faq-item h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .5rem; }
    .faq-item p { margin: 0; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .winner-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .price-callout { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
    }
</style>

<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/vs">Compare</a>
    <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="cta-nav">Get started free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="vs-badge">Honest Comparison</div>
  <h1>SocialProof vs <span>Endorsal</span></h1>
  <p>Both tools automate testimonial collection. One starts free. The other charges $29/mo before you've collected your first review.</p>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="hero-cta">Start free — no credit card needed</a>
</div>

<div style="text-align:center; padding: 0 2rem 3rem;">
  <div class="price-callout">
    <div class="item vouch">
      <div class="price">$0</div>
      <div class="label">SocialProof — Start free</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item other">
      <div class="price">$29/mo</div>
      <div class="label">Endorsal — Cheapest paid plan</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Feature-by-feature comparison</h2>
  <table class="compare-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Feature</th>
        <th>SocialProof</th>
        <th>Endorsal</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Free plan</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Free forever (1 widget)</td>
        <td class="no">✗ No free plan</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Starting price</td>
        <td class="yes">$0 free / $9/mo Pro</td>
        <td class="no">$29/mo</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Shareable collection link</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ One link, no friction</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Yes</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Embeddable widget</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Wall, carousel, badge</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Yes</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Text + photo testimonials</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Both</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Both</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Video testimonials</td>
        <td class="partial">Coming soon</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Yes (higher plans)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Approve before publishing</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Full moderation</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Yes</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Custom branding</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Pro plan</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Yes</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Shopify integration</td>
        <td class="partial">Coming soon</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Native app</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>API access</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Included</td>
        <td class="partial">Higher plans only</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Setup time</td>
        <td class="yes">Under 5 minutes</td>
        <td class="partial">15–30 minutes</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>No-code embed</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ One script tag</td>
        <td class="yes">✓ Yes</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Who wins for each use case?</h2>
  <div class="winner-grid">
    <div class="winner-card vouch">
      <h3>✅ Choose SocialProof if you…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Want to start collecting testimonials today, for free</li>
        <li>Run a small business or solo practice with limited budget</li>
        <li>Need something set up in under 5 minutes</li>
        <li>Want one shareable link you can send in any email or DM</li>
        <li>Don't want to pay $29/mo just to test whether it works</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="winner-card other">
      <h3>Consider Endorsal if you…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Run a Shopify store and need native cart integration</li>
        <li>Need video testimonials today (not willing to wait)</li>
        <li>Have a larger team needing multiple seats</li>
        <li>Budget isn't a constraint and you want a mature platform</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="savings-box">
    <h3>💰 The math: SocialProof saves you $240–$600/year</h3>
    <p>Endorsal's cheapest plan is $29/mo ($348/yr). SocialProof Pro is $9/mo ($108/yr) — or free forever for 1 widget. That's a saving of $240 per year on Pro, and $348/year if you stay on the free plan. For a small business, that's real money.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Why small businesses choose SocialProof over Endorsal</h2>
  <p style="color:#444; line-height:1.7;">
    Endorsal is a solid product, but it was built for established businesses with a marketing budget. The $29/mo entry price creates a significant barrier for freelancers, solo practitioners, and small business owners who are just starting to think about social proof.
  </p>
  <p style="color:#444; line-height:1.7;">
    SocialProof was designed from the ground up for exactly this audience. The core insight: <strong>collecting your first 10 testimonials should be free.</strong> You share one link with your best customers, they fill in a short form, you review and approve, then embed the widget on your site. No monthly commitment required to get started.
  </p>
  <p style="color:#444; line-height:1.7;">
    When you're ready to scale — custom branding, unlimited widgets, priority support — that's what Pro is for, at $9/mo. Not $29.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Can I really use SocialProof for free?</h3>
    <p>Yes. The free plan is free forever — not a trial. You get 1 active widget, unlimited testimonial collection, and moderation controls. There's no expiry and no credit card required to sign up.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Does SocialProof have a Shopify app like Endorsal?</h3>
    <p>Native Shopify app integration is on the roadmap. Right now, you can embed the SocialProof widget on any Shopify store using our JavaScript snippet — it takes about 2 minutes to add via your theme editor.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>How long does it take to get my first testimonial with SocialProof?</h3>
    <p>Most users collect their first testimonial within 24 hours of signing up. You create a collection link, send it to a happy customer, they fill in the form (takes ~2 minutes), and you approve it. That's the whole flow.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Can I migrate my Endorsal testimonials to SocialProof?</h3>
    <p>Yes. You can manually re-enter testimonials or ask us to help with a bulk import. Email us at hello@socialproof.dev and we'll handle it for you.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>What happens if I collect more testimonials than my plan allows?</h3>
    <p>You can collect unlimited testimonials on any plan. Plan limits only apply to the number of active embeddable widgets — not how many testimonials you can hold in your account.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="bottom-cta">
  <h2>Ready to try the free alternative to Endorsal?</h2>
  <p>No credit card. No 14-day trial countdown. Just a free account that works.</p>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register">Create free account →</a>
</div>

</Base>
